As documented in the [jOOQ code generation manual][1] and also throughout the [third party plugin documentation][2], you have to specify an `inputSchema` if you don&#39;t want the code generator to generate *all* schemas.

Specifically:

```
database.apply {
    name = &quot;org.jooq.meta.h2.H2Database&quot;
    inputSchema = &quot;PUBLIC&quot;
    ...
}
```


